company_name: JOHANN KNÜPPEL, OBST- UND GEMÜSEGROSSHANDEL E.K., INHABER HANS-PETER MÜLLER
information: The company JOHANN KNÜPPEL, OBST- UND GEMÜSEGROSSHANDEL E.K., INHABER HANS-PETER MÜLLER, is a Wholesaler, founded in 1900, which operates in the Fruits and vegetables - import-export industry. It is based in Martensrade, Germany.
